{"type": "article", "id": 24164, "title": "花式吐司切割器", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-21T07:00:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021254528ZKj7SosW56kMg3l.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">如何让早餐做得有趣是很多上班族都在思考的问题，这款花式切割器可以在吐司中间切割出一些小块，装点在吐司旁边，做成鱼、鸡、小熊等动物的形状，灵活而有趣。中间空出来的地方则可煎上一个鸡蛋，一个营养的爱心早餐就此达成。产品目前正在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1317510995/bready-made-a-bread-cutter-for-creative-meals?token=394ef578\">这里是众筹链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125448n9eGMw6lpZq3uaHd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66323529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125448m1EsJ8DClfYWgdIx.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4359352\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125450riYz7tXpbOmUk8B4.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.43888071\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021254511KGpr0axnt86Hbej.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.10588235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021254520POmDLFwpMRhcIyf.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}